{"tid":230692,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"額頭粒粒 多印","createTime":"2017-05-05T14:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T18:18:13.000Z","uid":39825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3601960110d9e20348084f9f9876da99969ce240","tid":230692,"uid":39825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"想問下各位巴絲<br />\n我個額頭有好多粒粒<br />\n之後自己唧到好多印<br />\n應該點搞好<br />\n<br />\n睇醫生定去美容院好啲？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/220502_f72c64eec95ef5cc5f976cbfee4b489f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F220502_f72c64eec95ef5cc5f976cbfee4b489f.jpg&h=05f5c1ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62dde04f2b5525d9498d55bb5f6154d1a2f3d8dc","tid":230692,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"1 早睡早起 戒濃味 戒多油 戒零食<br />\n2 飲多啲水 做多啲帶氧運動<br />\n3 天然成份洗面奶<br />\n<br />\n其他乜鳩都係治標唔治本 掉錢落咸水海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75e7dcde959a34b32a9b7287ae04a3d6b531a27","tid":230692,"uid":278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:13:27.000Z","msg":"放返d頭髮落黎<br />\n睇唔到睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b19a0aaa051ade02805104746969eb426c12b3","tid":230692,"uid":39825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放返d頭髮落黎<br />\n睇唔到睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時好熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想解決"},{"pid":"3e4e4dd7b399d8c5e33385a7895f30eccc64f862","tid":230692,"uid":39825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1 早睡早起 戒濃味 戒多油 戒零食<br />\n2 飲多啲水 做多啲帶氧運動<br />\n3 天然成份洗面奶<br />\n<br />\n其他乜鳩都係治標唔治本 掉錢落咸水海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔算遲訓 12-1 點訓<br />\n係有時打通胡機<br />\n食都算清淡啦 因為我有gym 餐單<br />\n水都算正常<br />\n之前有用洗面奶 發覺用開會易生暗右啲<br />\n<br />\n我想清一清返啲印用粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e641811ca0572bf8d6c633068d625edbe9b20889","tid":230692,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"唔好染髮<br />\n唔好留陰 基本"},{"pid":"00779a0e51de1f0cb00997c6f0fc6bcc3086c2cc","tid":230692,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:25:57.000Z","msg":"好小事啫，早d訓就得"},{"pid":"6c2d6a2381d6769e0e9a5e59a8eb859e5a8b6294","tid":230692,"uid":39825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好染髮<br />\n唔好留陰 基本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但依家好多印喎 <br />\n唔留陰好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fbd31858b47990e1f8dbb9914872f548092878","tid":230692,"uid":102407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:06:50.000Z","msg":"果酸/水楊酸+維他命c類產品"},{"pid":"4c3bbdcc4b542cf53660712e358c72f1d5cd3ddb","tid":230692,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:11:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好染髮<br />\n唔好留陰 基本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但依家好多印喎 <br />\n唔留陰好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bloc